[This has been a tough year for animal owners facing vesicular stomatitis. It has been widespread in both Colorado and Texas. It is good news to know that most of the quarantines have been lifted.

Readers are encouraged to read my comments on ProMED-mail post 20140927.2811014 for more information on the vesicular stomatitis virus.

The state of Colorado can be located on the HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map at https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=2978287,209. - Mod.TG]
